 of the Constitution's role in the United States today.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Mrz 2024) 0aConstitutional historyzUnited States. 0aConstitutional lawzUnited States. 0aJudgeszUnited StatesvBiography. 0aJudges-United States-Biography. 0aMarshall, John,-1755-1835-Political and social views. 4aPhilosophy : American Philosophy. 4aPolitics and Law : Constitutional Studies. 4aPolitics and Law : Political Science. 4aPolitics and Law : Political Theory. 7aPOLITICAL SCIENCE / American Government / Judicial Branch.2bisacsh40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9781438474427?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781438474427423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781438474427/original  aGBV-deGruyter-alles